= PUPPET MODULE:
  perl

== REQUIREMENTS:

=== Platform and Application Environment:

Tested on Ubuntu 12.04. May work on other platforms, esp Ubuntu/Debian.

== USAGE:

# Simple default install

class { 'perl' : }
include perl

# Use external data for packages

class { 'perl' : packages => hiera('some_other_packages') }

# Change the list of packages to install

class { 'perl' : packages => [ 'other_package', 'another_package' ] }

# Ensure the packages are not installed

class { 'perl' : installed => false }

== CAVEATS:

Currently no CPAN support. Only Debian package support

